{{DISPLAYTITLE:Scroll_Texture_Down}} {{Special|103|speed [, flags]|Scrolling|Texture, 1Down|use=line}}
* ''speed'': Speed to scroll * ''flags'': Which parts of the [[linedef]] should scroll
Scrolls a texture downwards.
''flags'' can be a combination of the following values:
* 1: scroll the upper texture * 2: scroll the mid texture * 4: scroll the lower texture
For compatibility, 0 and any value larger than 7 will scroll all parts of the linedef.
==Examples== {{noexamples}}
== Conversions from linedef types == The following Doom map format types can be converted as : {| {{prettytable}} !Type!!Conversion!!Trigger |- |{{icon|Strife}} 143:Scrolling Wall Down Triple Speed || Scroll_Texture_Down ({{xlat|SCROLL_UNIT*3}}) || |- |{{icon|EDGE}} 424:Scrolling Wall Down || Scroll_Texture_Down ({{xlat|SCROLL_UNIT}}) || |}
